WEBVTT

01:51:03.459 --> 01:51:04.293
How can I not mind?

01:51:04.751 --> 01:51:07.001
Do you think everything is up to you?
It won't happen.

01:51:07.501 --> 01:51:11.376
Sir, he killed my mother...
how can I let him go, sir?

01:51:11.709 --> 01:51:13.001
Who do you think he is?

01:51:13.418 --> 01:51:16.834
Big Bull! we need to arrest him,
then take him to court... there's a process.

01:51:17.334 --> 01:51:19.043
If that's the case, it will take ten years for
justice to be served.

01:51:19.918 --> 01:51:21.376
I have other plans

01:51:21.501 --> 01:51:22.334
What plans?

01:51:22.501 --> 01:51:26.001
Once he is caught, I'll put a mark
on his forehead and chop off his head.

01:51:26.459 --> 01:51:27.459
No. No!

01:51:27.501 --> 01:51:29.668
Sir... if you say no, my blood will boil.

01:51:29.709 --> 01:51:31.709
Will it? What will you do if it boils?
